About universAAL LDDI KNX Refinement driver for Datapoint Type 1.* to ISO 11073-10471 device

Encoding and decoding of KNX Datapoint Types 1.* with Format B1. Is registered as OSGI driver service in the framework registry. This refinement driver maps and creates a suitable device from ISO 11073-10471 specification and registers it in the OSGi registry.
